Upload:
- Submit pictures of verifications and certain other documents and upload them to DTA.

My Info: You can now update your contact information.
- Request for changes to residential and mailing address.
- Update or add Primary phone number.
- Update or add Primary email address.
- Opt-in/opt-out of Email notifications.
- Opt-in/opt-out of Text Message notifications.

Activity:
- You can now view notices sent by DTA to you and members in your household under "Notices" section in Activity tab.

Home Screen:
- New navigation menu with easy access to all key components.

Other Features:
- Request income verification letter (proof of DTA benefits) to be mailed to you.
- Link to Farmers' markets location search.

Coming Soon: Real time EBT Balance will provide up to date and real time EBT balance from your EBT card.
